More Details on NEW Membership Tier!

Last week's news included info about the new upcoming tier Premiere Go!

More Info has now become available on how the new tier will work.

 

Guests who are insiders, if they visit at least 8 times or earn 5000 points they will
be rewarded the new tier Premiere Go! Beginning Jan 1st, some guests may receive the
upgrade based on their visits for 2024! The upgrade will last for the remaining 2025 year
and all of 2026 when they receive the free upgrade to the new tier. For guests to keep
their tier for 2027 they must re-qualify by earning an additional 5000 points or visit 8 times
within the calendar year! Look at last week's news page for more info on Premiere Go!

 



Additional Information

New Chicken Tenders (Tyson Branded)

If you haven't already seen in workplace we are switching to a

New type of chicken tender. For any remaining old stock please use the fryer option

'Tendies', when we run out of old stock please switch to the new style.

When cooking the new tenders use the Fryer option 'New Tenders' as it has a

New cook time of 5 minutes. When making bulk orders (more than one at a time)
use the 'Tenders Bulk' option as this add 30 seconds to ensure proper cooking.

Always Check the internal temperature of the chicken with a thermometer to be at 165° before serving


New Pretzel Bites

We have received our new Bavarian Bites. They are much softer and bigger sized bites.
Since they are bigger, the portion size has been slightly reduced.
15 bites now come in an order instead of the traditional 20
